<div class=3D"panel"><h3 style=3D"text-align:center">Did you know?</h3>
<p class=3D"didyouknow">
Samuel Langhorne Clemens was one of the most famous Americans of the 1800s.=
 The author of several books, including <span style=3D"font-style:italic;">=
The Adventures of Tom Sawyer</span>, he is best remembered by his pen name,=
 Mark Twain. This name may have come from his work as a steamboat pilot. To=
 steer the steamboat, the water needed to be 2 fathoms deep, or "by the mar=
k, twain" to be in safe water.
</p></div>
